Interface Summary
FilterRule<T> This is the interface of filter rules.
Function<I,O> This interface defines functions.
LatticeListener<T> This interface defines listeners used in Lattice.
Namer<T> This class defines a namer that can give names for a specified type of elements.
Order<T> This interface defines a binary relation.
Semiring<T> This interface defines a semiring (R, +, *, 0, 1) where R is a set of elements, + (plus) is a binary operation, * (multiplication) is a binary operation, 0 is the identity of +, and 1 is the identity of *.
